OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fspells of sunshine around this
OL,7,Fevening, with showers slowly dying
OL,8,Fout, before a band of cloud and rain
OL,9,Faccompanied by blustery winds spreads
OL,10,Feastward overnight. A milder night
OL,11,Fthan of late.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FOvernight rain clearing to
OL,14,Fthe northeast, leaving a mix of sunny
OL,15,Fspells and blustery showers on
OL,16,FTuesday. Some of the showers
OL,17,Fpotentially heavy with a risk of
OL,18,Fthunder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
