OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FLighter winds on Wednesday but still
OL,7,Fwith a risk of showers. Turning drier
OL,8,Fand brighter on Thursday, with more
OL,9,Fsunshine by Friday. Feeling much
OL,10,Fwarmer with temperatures above average.
